casebody.data:
DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

91-417. Findlay/Hancock Cty. Bar Assn. v. Leatherman.

On response to show cause order. No action will be taken by the court at this time.

Douglas, J., would dismiss the show cause order. Resnick, J., would permit Michael J. Leatherman to continue installment payments. Moyer, C.J., would hold respondent in contempt.
